originalText.text: Before working with Anastasia, I felt as though I was floating through life aimlessly. I felt very capable, but had no clue where I wanted to direct my life. Working with her was truly a life changing experience. Anastasia challenged me to discover deeper answers and truths about myself that were difficult to find at first, but became more apparent throughout my journey. I came in lost, and came out of this coaching experience with a specific plan, and a list of goals I'm proud to chase after. I would highly recommend working with Anastasia if you are serious about changing your life and ready to do the work to start doing things you really love to do.

originalText.text: Before I started working with Anastasia I felt "lost" and unhappy in my current career path. I was looking to find some direction to be both happy AND successful in my career. After working with Anastasia I have gained increased confidence in making career decisions. She gave me great "tools" to use for researching professions. She has good insight and gives great advice. This helped me to have new awareness of opportunities. She is very understanding and non-judgemental. She is very easy to talk to. I would recommend working with Anastasia to anyone thinking about making a career change or looking to find happiness and passion in their life's work.

originalText.text: I loved everything about our life coaching sessions with Anastasia! Being a very visual, creative person it is hard to put everything into concrete steps and find the motivation behind it. Every session gave me a lot of clarity and passion to move forward, inspired and helped me to move into the direction I really want! I was able to finally understand and feel what to do professionally! I am very thankful to Anastasia for that. She is also genuinely positive, driven and has your best interest at heart!
